text: Gabi Luncă (16 October 1938 – 2 April 2021) was a Romanian singer and musician. She was born in Vărbilău, Prahova County, Romania. Luncă was a lăutari musician and folk singer. She died of COVID-19 in Bucharest. She was 82 years old. == References == Category:1938 births Category:2021 deaths Category:Romanian singers Category:Deaths from the COVID-19 pandemic in Bucharest
title: Gabi Luncă
